V0610_01_00_00_0.text:
I can steal anything for you.
If you can afford my fee.

V0610_01_00_01_0.text: You sure you want to Duel instead of talking it out?

V0610_01_00_02_0.text: The bigger the threat, the greater the reward.

V0610_01_00_03_0.text: Can't wait to see what tricks you have in store for me!

V0610_01_00_04_0.text:
I love a good challenge.
Let's Duel!

V0610_01_00_05_0.text: As a hacker, I've come too far to leave with nothing!

V0610_01_00_06_0.text:
Been a while, Playmaker.
And that cutie Ai is with you too!

V0610_01_00_07_0.text: I never expected to battle Varis in a place like this...

V0610_01_00_07_1.text: But if I'm gonna Duel, I'm gonna win!

V0610_01_00_08_0.text: His deck contains a powerful Link Monster.

V0610_01_00_08_1.text: The longer this Duel lasts, the worse position I'll be in!

V0610_01_00_09_0.text:
Oh hey now.
You changed your avatar back.

V0610_01_00_09_1.text: Did you also change your strategies for the better?

V0610_01_00_10_0.text: You do realize I know all your moves, right big bro?

V0610_01_00_11_0.text: I hope you're as talented as your best friend Playmaker.

V0610_03_00_00_0.text: Time to put the finishing touches on this Duel!

V0610_03_00_01_0.text: Your strategy is worthless if you don't get to play it!

V0610_03_00_04_0.text:
Look at all those splashy moves!
You should be proud!

V0610_03_00_05_0.text:
You're playing well.
But nothing I didn't expect.

V0610_05_00_00_0.text:
This is my chance...
I won't get a second crack at this!

V0610_06_01_01_0.text: I don't think that's going to help.

V0610_06_01_02_0.text: I can't let you do that.

V0610_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0610_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0610_11_10_01_0.text: I’ll create a circuit that links the known with the unknown!

V0610_11_10_02_0.text: I’ll create a circuit that links the known with the unknown!

V0610_11_10_02_1.text:
I set my monsters in the Link Arrows!
Link the circuit!

V0610_16_00_01_0.text: Looks like your bank account's empty.

V0610_21_00_00_0.text: When I win, I'll be on easy street!

V0610_21_00_01_0.text: Defeating a superstar like you will do wonders for my rep.

V0610_21_00_03_0.text: I've put together a pretty good lineup.

V0610_21_00_04_0.text: I should be able to survive until my next turn...

V0610_21_00_05_0.text:
Be careful.
I'm not out of moves yet!

V0610_28_00_00_0.text: I hope I run into you again sometime!

V0610_28_00_01_0.text: Victory loves me more than you.

V0610_28_00_02_0.text: I get the feeling I'll be seeing more of you, hun.

V0610_28_00_03_0.text: There's nothing I can't hack - from databases to Dueling!

V0610_28_00_04_0.text:
Right place, right time.
Just the wrong opponent.

V0610_28_00_05_0.text: You'd be worth my time - if you had more skill and riches.

V0610_28_00_06_0.text:
They can take everything.
But don't let 'em take your heart.

V0610_28_00_07_0.text:
Sorry, Kenneth.
Looks like I'm the smart one in the family.

V0610_28_00_08_0.text: You may be brave, but you don't know how to battle!

V0610_28_00_09_0.text: I thought Playmaker's sidekick would put up more of a fight.

V0610_29_00_00_0.text:
I couldn't hack it this time.
But I'm not giving up!

V0610_29_00_01_0.text: I prepped for this Duel, but you played better than me.

V0610_29_00_02_0.text:
I lost all my monsters...
And I call myself a pro.

V0610_29_00_03_0.text: When you can Summon monsters that easily, I have no chance.

V0610_29_00_04_0.text: You've caught my attention - whether you wanted to or not.

V0610_29_00_05_0.text:
You weren't scared of any of my strategies...
Interesting!

V0610_29_00_06_0.text: You sure know how to show a girl a good time.

V0610_29_00_06_1.text: Ai, want me to introduce you to some cute little widgets?

V0610_29_00_07_0.text: Varis was toying with me the whole Duel...

V0610_29_00_08_0.text: How was he able to get that terrifying card?

V0610_29_00_10_0.text: You win the bounty, big bro.

V0610_33_00_01_0.text: You're not the only one with a Skill!

V0610_33_00_02_0.text: No data is safe from a hacker like me!

V0610_33_00_03_0.text:
I'll use my Skill!
Secret Cure!

V0610_30_00_00_0.text: I'll stop lecturing you - even though you need one.

V0610_30_00_01_0.text: It took me all night to build this deck.

V0610_30_00_02_0.text:
Don't compare me to those riffraff.
I'm much more charming.

V0610_34_00_00_0.text: Not every problem can be solved with my hacking skills.

V0610_34_00_01_0.text: Without skills or talent, you'll never catch my attention.

V0610_34_00_03_0.text: You think those moves will trick me into making a mistake?

V0610_34_00_05_0.text: Thanks. But that has nothing to do with this Duel.

V0610_34_00_06_0.text: This is when my hacking skills come in handy.

V0610_34_00_07_0.text: That's not a pretty card at all.

V0610_34_00_08_0.text: I still have a chance if I can get the right effect!

V0610_34_00_09_0.text: You have a deal if you triple my fee!

V0610_34_00_10_0.text: How can you not be worried about my Trap Card?

V0610_34_00_11_0.text:
You should take a nap.
Then you can dream about winning.

V0610_34_00_12_0.text: I have a great idea - but it's risky...

V0610_34_00_13_0.text: I deleted all footage of this Duel.

V0610_32_00_01_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links!
It's time to link into the VRAINS!

V0610_35_00_00_0.text: No secret's safe from me - for the right price.

V0610_35_00_01_0.text: From hacking to Dueling - there's nothing I can't do!

V0610_36_00_00_0.text: If you wanna win this for us, I'm not gonna complain.

V0610_36_00_02_0.text:
Be careful.
Their cards are tough to deal with.

V0610_36_00_03_0.text: Let me see if your game's improved.

V0610_36_00_04_0.text: Show 'em why you're the best partner anyone can have.

V0610_36_00_05_0.text: Teach 'em to never mess with family!

Altergeist Camouflage!

V0610_08_00_00_1.text: I equip it on my Altergeist monster!

V0610_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Altergeist Manifestation!

V0610_08_00_02_0.text: I banish Altergeist Manifestation from my Graveyard!

V0610_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Altergeist Revitalization!

V0610_08_00_04_0.text: I banish Altergeist Revitalization from my Graveyard!

V0610_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Altergeist Emulatelf!

V0610_08_00_05_1.text: I Special Summon this card as an Effect Monster!

V0610_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Altergeist Failover!

V0610_08_00_08_0.text: I banish Altergeist Failover from my Graveyard!

V0610_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Altergeist Protocol!

V0610_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Altergeist Haunted Rock!

V0610_08_00_12_0.text: I activate Altergeist Haunted Rock's effect!

V0610_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Personal Spoofing!

V0610_08_00_15_1.text: I know this isn't what you wanted to see.

V0610_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Infinite Impermanence!

V0610_08_00_17_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Twin Twisters!

V0610_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Mistaken Arrest!

Queen of the fairies!
Invite your foes to your nightmare!

V0610_13_00_01_0.text:
Come on out!
Link 4 Altergeist Adminia!

V0610_37_00_01_0.text: Manifesting from the edge of nightmares!

V0610_37_00_02_0.text: Rise from your eternal slumber to break the barrier!

V0610_13_00_05_0.text: Enter this existence, Level 6 Altergeist Dragvirion!

Altergeist Marionetter!
